---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Support" description="Give to Pear Tree Community School. Your gift bridges the gap between what families can pay and what it costs to provide a liberatory education.">

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="bg-forest-900 text-white">
    <div class="section-padding py-16 md:py-24">
      <p class="text-pear-400 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Support Pear Tree</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight max-w-3xl">
        Invest in education that transforms.
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tuition Gap Message -->
  <section class="bg-pear-50 border-b border-pear-100">
    <div class="section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-earth-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          At Pear Tree, <strong>80% of our families receive financial aid</strong> because we believe every child deserves a liberatory education — regardless of what their family can pay. Tuition alone covers only a fraction of what it costs to deliver our Montessori, social justice, and nature-based curriculum. <strong>Your gift directly bridges the gap</strong> between what families can pay and what it costs to educate each child.
        </p>
        <p class="text-forest-700 font-serif text-xl font-bold mt-6 italic">
          When you give to Pear Tree, you are making it possible for a child to stay.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Give Section -->
  <section id="give" class="section-padding scroll-mt-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="section-heading text-center mb-4">The Pear Tree Annual Fund</h2>
      <p class="section-subheading text-center mx-auto mb-12">
        Every gift, at any level, sustains the education our students depend on.
      </p>

      <!-- Giving Tiers -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-12">
        {[
          { name: 'Seeds', amount: 'Up to $99', impact: 'Provides art supplies for a classroom for one month' },
          { name: 'Roots', amount: '$100 – $499', impact: 'Funds a field trip for an entire class' },
          { name: 'Branches', amount: '$500 – $999', impact: 'Equips a classroom with new Montessori materials' },
          { name: 'Canopy', amount: '$1,000 – $2,499', impact: 'Provides professional development for a teacher' },
          { name: 'Orchard', amount: '$2,500 – $4,999', impact: 'Funds a semester of aftercare scholarships' },
          { name: 'Founders\' Circle', amount: '$5,000+', impact: 'Provides a full-year scholarship for one student' },
        ].map(tier => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-earth-100 hover:border-forest-300 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-lg text-forest-700">{tier.name}</h3>
            <p class="text-pear-600 font-semibold text-sm mt-1">{tier.amount}</p>
            <p class="text-earth-600 text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">{tier.impact}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- Donation Form Placeholder -->
      <div id="donate" class="bg-forest-50 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-forest-100 text-center">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Make Your Gift</h3>
        <p class="text-earth-600 mb-6">Choose a one-time or monthly contribution at any amount.</p>

        <!-- Donorbox embed will go here -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-earth-200 min-h-[200px] flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-earth-400 text-sm mb-4">[ Donorbox donation form will be embedded here ]</p>
            <p class="text-earth-500 text-xs">
              To embed: Replace this div with<br />
              <code class="bg-earth-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs">&lt;script src="https://donorbox.org/widget.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-xs text-earth-400 mt-6">
          Your gift may be tax-deductible. Contact us for details about our fiscal sponsorship arrangement.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Monthly Giving -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-forest-50 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-forest-100">
          <h2 class="section-heading">Join The Orchard</h2>
          <p class="text-earth-600 text-sm mb-2">Our monthly giving community</p>
          <p class="text-earth-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Monthly donors are the roots that sustain Pear Tree year-round. By joining The Orchard, you provide predictable, sustained support that allows us to plan ahead and serve more families.
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-6">
            {[
              { amount: '$10/mo', label: 'Art supplies' },
              { amount: '$25/mo', label: 'Student materials' },
              { amount: '$50/mo', label: 'Program support' },
              { amount: '$100/mo', label: 'Scholarship fund' },
              { amount: '$250/mo', label: 'Faculty development' },
              { amount: 'Custom', label: 'Any amount helps' },
            ].map(tier => (
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 text-center border border-forest-100">
                <p class="font-semibold text-forest-700">{tier.amount}</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-earth-500 mt-1">{tier.label}</p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>

          <a href="#donate" class="btn-primary block text-center">Start Monthly Giving</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Other Ways to Give -->
  <section class="section-padding">
    <h2 class="section-heading text-center mb-12">Other Ways to Support</h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-pear-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-pear-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M15.75 10.5V6a3.75 3.75 0 1 0-7.5 0v4.5m11.356-1.993 1.263 12c.07.665-.45 1.243-1.119 1.243H4.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.12-1.243l1.264-12A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 5.513 7.5h12.974c.576 0 1.059.435 1.119 1.007ZM8.625 10.5a.375.375 0 1 1-.75 0 .375.375 0 0 1 .75 0Zm7.5 0a.375.375 0 1 1-.75 0 .375.375 0 0 1 .75 0Z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-lg mb-2">Classroom Wishlist</h3>
        <p class="text-earth-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Purchase specific items our classrooms need — from Montessori materials to art supplies — shipped directly to the school.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-forest-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-forest-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M20.25 14.15v4.25c0 1.094-.787 2.036-1.872 2.18-2.087.277-4.216.42-6.378.42s-4.291-.143-6.378-.42c-1.085-.144-1.872-1.086-1.872-2.18v-4.25m16.5 0a2.18 2.18 0 0 0 .75-1.661V8.706c0-1.081-.768-2.015-1.837-2.175a48.114 48.114 0 0 0-3.413-.387m4.5 8.006c-.194.165-.42.295-.673.38A23.978 23.978 0 0 1 12 15.75c-2.648 0-5.195-.429-7.577-1.22a2.016 2.016 0 0 1-.673-.38m0 0A2.18 2.18 0 0 1 3 12.489V8.706c0-1.081.768-2.015 1.837-2.175a48.111 48.111 0 0 1 3.413-.387m7.5 0V5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 13.5 3h-3a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25v.894m7.5 0a48.667 48.667 0 0 0-7.5 0"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-lg mb-2">Employer Matching</h3>
        <p class="text-earth-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Many Bay Area employers — Google, Apple, Meta, Salesforce — match charitable gifts up to $10,000/year. Double your impact.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-earth-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-earth-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M10.05 4.575a1.575 1.575 0 1 0-3.15 0v3m3.15-3v-1.5a1.575 1.575 0 0 1 3.15 0v1.5m-3.15 0 .075 5.925m3.075.75V4.575m0 0a1.575 1.575 0 0 1 3.15 0V15M6.9 7.575a1.575 1.575 0 1 0-3.15 0v8.175a6.75 6.75 0 0 0 6.75 6.75h2.018a5.25 5.25 0 0 0 3.712-1.538l1.732-1.732a5.25 5.25 0 0 0 1.538-3.712l.003-2.024a.668.668 0 0 0-.668-.668 1.667 1.667 0 0 1-1.667-1.667V8.67"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-lg mb-2">Volunteer</h3>
        <p class="text-earth-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Join our community as a volunteer. Parents contribute required annual volunteer hours — and we welcome community members too.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Walk-a-Thon -->
  <section class="bg-forest-700 text-white">
    <div class="section-padding text-center">
      <p class="text-pear-400 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Annual Event</p>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold mb-4">5th Annual Walk-a-Thon</h2>
      <p class="text-forest-200 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-2">
        April 26, 2026 &middot; Oakland Tech High School Track &amp; Field
      </p>
      <p class="text-forest-300 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Join families, students, and supporters for our biggest community fundraiser of the year.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary bg-pear-500 hover:bg-pear-600 text-charcoal font-bold">Get Involved</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
